Body: Excellent question, There are a few strategies for this.  1. We will establish partnerships (Large GYMS) where we will offer them profitable merchant services for accepting the token in the GYMs. 2. Users will be able to sponsor GYMs and earn a percent of all the mining in that location by requesting approvals and therefor start a GYM partnership. 3. Others will be forced into partnership once users start telling them that they should accept the product to enable mining at their location. Otherwise, they may go somewhere else to exercise.

Title: ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ [ICO]GymRewards - Get Paid for Exercising! ğŸ‹ï¸â€â™‚ï¸ [BOUNTYHIVE.IO] ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥
Body: What is GYM Rewards? The GYM Rewards project consists of an entire solution to support getting paid for exercising. From the Blockchain that supports Proof of Exercise to the GYM Rewards Exchange for gymnasiums and other partners to come and exchange GYM Tokens. There is no need to wait for exchanges to support GYM and there is no need to take the risk of getting stuck with useless tokens. The GYM Rewards app is a patent pending app that rewards you for exercising at the GYM by introducing Proof of Exercise to the blockchain. The more you exercise at the GYM, the more GYM Coins you will earn. GYM Coins are redeemable at your local participating gyms and will be tradable at participating cryptocurrency exchanges.

Body: Thanks for you question.  1. We are going to earn money from transaction fees. The transactions from App to Exchanges, App to App and from App to GYMs will generate a transaction fee. These fee goes towards token holders according to their market share. We as founders OWN tokens too. 2. We also believe that some gymnasiums who are participants may not want to deal with trading their tokens or the cryptocurrency world at all. we will become their merchant. 3. WE are also launching an tooken exchange to support partners and customers. There are transaction fees there also, unless customers hold 5000 GYMS or more.  Hope this helps.
